												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "A prison. Shadows flit over the prison’s walls by candlelight. A scream. Shot of mind flayer, wearing the garments we later find in the Elfsong Tavern (garments that disguise its true form) suckling on a criminal’s brain in its cell. The door has been broken open by its psionic strength. "
