								"editorData": [
									{
										"data": [
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "AnimationTags"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[LILI] Adventurer walks up to Moonrise with a map, headache, and in next cut he's strapped ot a chair, and a mindflayer approaches and puts a tadpole in his eye"
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "Attitude"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Default"
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "A boot stomps on a jutting piece of land (like the final step to get to the top of Everest.) The other boot follows. The adventurer has stopped there. A map in his hand. He's arrived: Moonrise Towers (before the shadow-curse.)\r\n\r\nCut to: mind flayer approaching the back of a board on which the adventurer is strapped and struggling. The mind flayer carries a tadpole (throwback to intro cinematic.) Closeup of the adventurer's eye as the tadpole goes in. Fade to black to screams of the adventurer. Fade in: Shot of the same room, clasps being undone on the board. A naked mind flayer rises - the Emperor. "
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicObjects"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
