													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Shot that pans out from the Emperor, showing it to be one among many (though wearing its distinctive garb). Non-mindmeld Emperor’s hand waves, wiping away the image, revealing it standing there before us. Mindmeld over. "
												}
